{"tid":1395530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係仆街仔 我淆底","createTime":"2019-08-01T19:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:19:28.000Z","uid":137632,"like":11,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"352cf33c365df95ebdcfb936736d6d4388fd9c64","tid":1395530,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:01:56.000Z","msg":"自從一個又一個義士比人拉左<br />\n<br />\n我就諗 下一個係咪到自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我驚係街比人打都報唔到警<br />\n我驚就咁普通返工都比差佬屈鳩我<br />\n我驚無啦啦比人入屋搜 搞到我屋企人<br />\n<br />\n我依個禮拜冇一日瞓到<br />\n<br />\n我禮拜六日可能真係要左膠一下 剩係帶最基本既野出去行算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我承認我輸左比白色恐怖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家禮拜六日真係唔好再比人拉<br />\n留力8月5 希望果日有人屌醒左我<br />\n<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d846c903d85cd77a230ee1a4ac57e7e946a014a","tid":1395530,"uid":137632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1503b51205acaf2c8f92fedb6cebf1cbe2e18e93","tid":1395530,"uid":137632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:02:38.000Z","msg":"對唔住手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa22541b6cda45e972fbd6fadef183223390d965","tid":1395530,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解香港可以恐怖成咁"},{"pid":"9f104272a6b591a0791b310e9ec6d60118e317a8","tid":1395530,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:03:34.000Z","msg":"那怕只有一個人睇到呢個post<br />\n可唔可以講下野 屌我又好 氹我都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid